quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  30,54,"Ko Alla woni taguﾉ熔 on e lo'ere, refti O waﾉ擁 ﾉ殿awo lo'ere nden cemmbe, refti O waﾉ擁 ﾉ殿awo cemmbe ﾉ容n lo'ere e puri(dandanndi). Himo taga ko O muuyi, Ko Kanko woni Annduﾉ熔, Hattanﾉ熔"
  30,55,"ﾃ疎lnde Darngal nal darotoo, bomﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n woonday ﾉ兎 ﾃｱiiﾉ殿ali si wanaa saanga. Ko wano nii ﾉ兎 wonanoo ferliseede (e goonga)"
  30,56,"Okkaaﾉ兎 ganndal e gomﾉ擁nal ﾉ兎n wi'a: \"Gomﾉ擁i on ﾃｱiiﾉ妬i e ko Alla winndi kon, haa ﾃｱalnde ummital. Ko ndee woni ﾃｱalaande ummital, kono onon on anndaano"
  30,57,"Nden ﾃｱalnde, ngantooji ﾉ擁n nafoytaa tooﾃｱuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, wanaa kamﾉ兎 woni ko ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬retee welayee [Alla]. @Corrected"
  30,58,"Gomﾉ擁i Men piyanii yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e nde Alquraanaa- re, kala misal. Pellet, si a addanii ﾉ兎 Aaya, ﾉ兎n yedduﾉ兎 wi'ay: \"On wonaali, si wanaa meerenteeﾉ兎"
  30,59,Ko wano nii Alla notira e ﾉ兎rﾉ容 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 anndaa
  30,60,"Muﾃｱﾃｱo, pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goona. Wata ﾉ兎 hoynuma ﾉ兎n hoyfine"
  31,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  31,2,"ﾆ各e, ko Aayeeje Deftere ﾃｱeﾃｱaande nden"
  31,3,Ko nde peewal e yurmeende wonannde moﾆｴﾆｴinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n
  31,4,"ﾉ兎n ﾃｱinnooﾉ兎 julde nden, ﾉ兎 totta aakkal on, hara kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 yananaaﾉ兎 (fii laakara)"
  31,5,"Ko ﾉ兎n woni e peewal immorde e Joomi maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎, ko kamﾉ兎 woni malaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n"
  31,6,"Hino woodi e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, soodiroowo mbeleeﾉ容 konnguﾉ擁 haa o majjira e laawol Alla ngol ko aldaa e ganndal, o jogitora (Aayeeje) ﾉ容n jalnitgol. ﾆ‘n ﾉ熔n, hino woodani ﾉ兎 lepte hoynooje"
  31,7,"Si Aayeeje Amen ﾉ容n janngaama e makko, o huccitira(runtora) townitaare, wa si tawii o nanaali ﾉ容, wa si tawii ko pahu woni e noppi makko. weltanir-mo lepte muusuﾉ容"
  31,8,"Pellet, ﾉ兎n gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 golli moﾆｴﾆｴi ﾉ擁n, hino woodani ﾉ兎 Aljannaaji neema"
  31,9,"Ko ﾉ兎 duumotooﾉ兎 ton, ﾉ蓉m ko fodoore Alla goongunde. Ko Kanko woni On Fooluﾉ熔, ﾃ粗eﾃｱuﾉ熔"
  31,10,"O tagirii kammuuli ﾉ擁n ko aldaa e tugaale, ﾉ容 yi'oton; O werlii ka leydi pelle fii wata ndi dillidu e mon; O saaki e mayri kala ruugayngel. Men jippiniri ndiyam ka kammu, Men fuﾉ擁ni e mayri kala nooneeji tedduﾉ擁"
  31,11,"ﾆ隔m ﾉ熔o ko tagu Alla. Hollee Lam ko ﾉ擁 (rewoton ﾉ擁n) gaanin Makko tagi?\" Si ko woni, tooﾃｱuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n no e majjere ﾉ殿nngunde"
  31,12,"Gomﾉ擁i Men okkii Luqmaan ﾃｱenﾆｴal: \"Wonnde yettu Alla. Kala yettuﾉ熔, haray ko hoore-makko o yettani; kala non yedduﾉ熔, anndu pellet, Alla ko Galo, Yettiniiﾉ熔"
  31,13,"Janto tuma Luqmaana wi'annoo geﾉ預l makko on, hari himo waajoo mo: \"Ko an ﾉ妬nngel am, wata a sirkan Alla. Pellet, sirku on ko tooﾃｱe mawﾉ容"
  31,14,"Men yamirii neﾉ遼預nke on [ﾉ熔ftagol] jibimﾉ兎 mo ﾉ兎n; yumma makko saawirii mo lo'ere e hoore lo'ere: entugol mo ngol, ko e nder duuﾉ妬 ﾉ擁ﾉ擁. \"Wonnde yettam e jinnaaﾉ兎 maa ﾉ兎n. Ko ka Am woni waﾉ葉inirde nden"
  31,15,"Si ﾉ兎 tiiﾉ溶orii ma fii sirkangol Lam e ko a alanaa ﾉ蓉m ganndal, wata a ﾉ熔fto ﾉ兎; wonndir e maﾉ橡兎 ka aduna ﾉ熔o moﾆｴﾆｴere. Jokku laawol on ruttiiﾉ熔 e Am. Refti ko ka Am woni ruttorde mon, Mi yeetitoo on, ko gollaynoﾉ熔n"
  31,16,"Ko an ﾉ妬nngel am, anndu ﾉ容n [golle bonﾉ容 maa moﾆｴﾆｴe], si fotii wa abbere, immorde e nenndi foﾃｱﾃｱe, ﾉ蓉m wona e fetere, maa ka kammuuli maa ka leydi, Alla artiray nde. Pellet, Alla ko Newiiﾉ熔, Humpitiiﾉ熔"
  31,17,"Ko an yo ﾉ妬nngel am, ﾃｱiiﾉ渡u julde nden, yamiraa moﾆｴﾆｴere, haﾉ預a ﾅ喫ﾃｱere(pankare), muﾃｱﾃｱo-ﾉ預a e ko heﾉ砥-maa. Pellet, ﾉ蓉m ko jeyaaﾉ蓉m e fiyakkuji mawﾉ擁. @Corrected"
  31,18,"Wata fal yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n yeeso maa ngon, wata a yahru ka leydi ﾃｱaaﾆｴagol. Pellet, Alla yiﾉ預a kala ﾃｱaaﾆｴotooﾉ熔 mantoo"
  31,19,"Hakindo e yahdu-maa ndun, joltinaa(ustu) hito maa ngon; ko ﾉ砥ri aﾃｱeede e hitooji ﾉ擁n, pellet, ko luukaadu mbabba"
  31,20,"E on yi'aali wonnde Alla eltanii on ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi? O huuﾉ妬tiri on neemaaji Makko feeﾃｱuﾉ擁 e suuﾉ擁iﾉ擁. Hino woodi e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, on wennjiroowo e fii Alla, ko aldaa e gannndal, wanaa peewal, wanaa Deftere jabunde"
  31,21,"Si ﾉ兎 wi'anaa:\"Jokkee kon ko Allah Jippini\", ﾉ兎 wi'a: \"Si ko woni, men jokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraaﾉ兎 amen ﾉ兎n\"; e hay si tawii seytaane wonii hino nodda ﾉ兎 e lepte dulboowe ngen"